subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams and her sister Venus, who have won 9 of the last 11 women’s singles titles at Wimbledon, were defeated, and No. 1-ranked Caroline Wozniacki also lost.
